                "endDateNew": "Present",
                "description": "<ul><li data-indent=\"1\"><p data-indent=\"1\">Led the architecture and implementation of a modular, policy-driven governance layer centralizing MCP access control and model I/O auditing, enabling consistent enforcement across agent workflows and reducing policy misconfiguration issues by ~50%.</p></li><li data-indent=\"1\"><p data-indent=\"1\">Designed multi-policy schemas and contract-driven TypeScript APIs, reducing integration-related regressions by 70% as AI interfaces evolved.</p></li><li data-indent=\"1\"><p data-indent=\"1\">Directed a system-wide refactor of React state management, eliminating 9+ redundant API calls and reducing initial load time by 11 seconds.</p></li><li data-indent=\"1\"><p data-indent=\"1\">Built a unified violations ingestion pipeline across LLM, MCP and RAG flows, standardizing cross-source observability reducing incident investigation time by approximately 40% through centralized event tracing.</p></li><li data-indent=\"1\"><p data-indent=\"1\">Developed D3-based interactive risk analytics dashboards to distinguish LLM vs. tool exposure patterns, accelerating policy debugging and strengthening audit traceability across 12+ policies.</p></li></ul><ul><li data-indent=\"1\"><p data-indent=\"1\">Optimized Docker-based frontend build pipeline on AWS EC2 by restructuring dependency installation strategy and leveraging layer caching, reducing development build times by ~10 minutes and accelerating backend frontend integration cycles.</p></li><li data-indent=\"1\"><p data-indent=\"1\">Developed role-based authentication and onboarding in Next.js with tenant-level access boundaries, eliminating post-login misrouting and reducing user-reported login errors by 30% within the first month post release.</p></li><li data-indent=\"1\"><p data-indent=\"1\">Coordinated cross-functional efforts between frontend, backend, and AI teams, integrating 3+ evolving model capabilities with governance constraints, maintaining consistent policy enforcement as the platform </p><p>introduced new tools and agents.</p></li></ul>",
                "employerLink": "https://copods.co/",
                "startDateNew": "07/2025",
                "showPlaceholder": false
